        "TileImage": "$($repository 6628072b-be73-4162-be32-a405928fea57).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Following Sapienza, your next operation takes you to Haven Island. The network that aided former Nazi&apos;s continues here. Your targets are Dexter Hooper, Indira Tandon, Paula Hansen, Jim Murphy, and Jonathan Marquis. Eliminate all five operatives who helped Padre Francesco and Paciano Giovanell provide safe passage and forged identities. Once complete, you will be ready to strike directly at the Nazi&apos;s themselves, good luck on this one, 47. I  dare say you are going to need it.",
